caption: Validate by opening in the editor
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/no-editor
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/no-editor/validate
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If you're not sure your hand-written profile is valid, open it in the
editor.  The validation banner at the top will be either green (''Profile
valid'') or red with a click-to-expand list of every problem — each entry
focuses the offending row when clicked.  Fix until green; close the editor;
the live-save will have re-written the JSON to its canonical form.

Hand-edited and editor-saved profiles are interchangeable; the editor reads
and writes the same shape.
